<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5331&amp;p=48208#p48208"><![CDATA[
Game for the nes and famicom are the same so there is no special rewiring if you take a famicom game and put in inside a nes cart. As long the hardware (mapper) and board are identical, it will work. <br /><br />I tested some nes game on my famicom dev board to make sure the dev cart is stable and had no issue.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=3559">Banshaku</a> — Tue Jun 23, 2009 6:53 pm</p><hr />
